offer antiquerestoration services she said 
before that it was just like any other small town ms 
dixon said it was like a ghost town 
like many small towns in rural america jamesports tax base was 
eroding and its agricultural economy was failing 
littrell said small towns often share common problems 
young people leave for higher paying jobs in cities 
