the idea for up with people stemmed from a 1965 summer youth 
conference in michigan said belk 
it was a time when you really had to give young people 
experience and there was no bigger challenge in the 60s than go 
give them a vehicle for their energy he said 
his tucson arizbased organization is independent nonprofit 
and educational and has no religious or political affiliations 
