<TEXT>
the man president bush wants to become the 
supreme courts 105th justice is hardly known outside new 
hampshire but his state court work and those who know him 
suggest david souter is a closetothevest conservative judge 
he does not pay any attention to the emotional political 
aspects of cases before him said stanley m brown a manchester 
nh lawyer and a former american bar association officer he 
doesnt go out blazing new pathways thats not his forte 
