a libel suit july 16 against the stuart news and its entertainment 
editor saying the newspaper published a campaign of falsehoods 
designed to wreck the societys image 
the nonprofit society headed by dorothy nabutovsky of palm 
city brings nationally known performing artists to stuart and is 
