seattle has gathered together fantastic musicians and 
singers chernov said one more time it demonstrates that music 
has no nationality 
to demonstrate further chernov sang the starspangled 
banner and john patrick napoleon in the opera sang the soviet 
national anthem for about 65000 people before a fourth of july 
fireworks show 
