a lifesaver jenkins said 
artistic success with war and peace will prove the 
capability of the seattle opera to pull off the largest and most 
complicated operas in the repertory without compromise bailey 
said theres no doubt in my mind that audiences are going to 
walk out completely overwhelmed 
