harold willens a businessmanpeacenik has 
turned a military base in his native soviet union into a childrens 
clothing factory 
there will be no money profits but willens 75 expects a 
return 
i see this not as a gift or charity but as a sound investment 
in the protection of everything ive talked about he said 
having hostility between two nuclear powers is a clear and 
present danger to my six grandchildren 
willens a multimillionaire who made his fortune in real estate 
said hes sunk about 400000 into the project by early july he 
said the factory was operating at 75 percent capacity turning out 
100000 pieces of clothing a month 
