it will be 39 wolfe said 
what we have is an aging society that is moving toward 
agelessness it is a worldwide movement we need to understand it 
to better be able to capitalize on it he said 
the term agelessness means that as a person grows older age 
loses significance in terms of influencing behavior wolfe said 
and what were concerned with in marketing is human 
behavior he said it is the stages of life that we really 
need to focus on not the ages of life 
