corporation has had to keep about half of the institutions assets 
it will take a major sales job to unload the sour loans real 
estate and junk bonds now in the governments hands 
most of the assets have been put on the books of the rtc not 
disposed of and there are hundreds more institutions they have 
to deal with barth said 
electionyear politics is complicating the administrations 
